# termquotes

A little CLI tool to record, categorize and display quotes.

## Install

`pip install --user termquotes`

## Usage

`termquotes --help`

#### Shell

In `.zshrc`

`termquotes get | cowsay -f vader | lolcat`

```
 ________________________________________
/ APIs should be easy to use and hard to \
\ misuse. -- Josh Bloch                  /
 ----------------------------------------
        \    ,-^-.
         \   !oYo!
          \ /./=\.\______
               ##        )\/\
                ||-----w||
                ||      ||

               Cowth Vader
```

